Ape VR Privacy policy

An IP address is a series of numbers connected to your internet
A Hardware ID is a series of letters and numbers to identify your device

1. Saved Data
A. your ip is saved to playfab/ApeVR account
B. your hardware id is saved in playfab to let you login to your playfab/AprVR account

2. why you save your data.
We save your data so it is possible to save in-game items to the game. We also use it so we can have moderation in our game.

2.Services we use
A. Playfab
B. Photon

3. why we use the services
A. we use these to make the gameplay experience fun and smooth

4. how to contact us.
If you have and concerns or questions about our privacy and policy email us here: apevrcontact@gmail.com or join our discord here: https://discord.gg/y8d5NnZq27

5. how to delete your collected data
you can delete our collected data by contacting us.
